parameters: Captain of the Guards "There he is! Surround him!"

Captain of the Guards "Chancellor Shif... You are hereby sentenced for the
crime of treason against the state."
Shif "What do you mean by that?!"

Captain of the Guards "There's no 'what' or 'how' about it. You've been
using the military for your own personal gain... Do you have any idea how
many soldiers have died needlessly because of you..."
Shif "Why... Why aren't they affected by the hypnotic magic..."

Captain of the Guards "It's useless... We've already taken precautions
against your hypnotic magic. Thanks to General Tros."
Captain of the Guards "Give it up! If you resist, you'll die right here."
Iburu: "We have no choice but to split up and search..."
